Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Total time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Checklist Completed across all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to be followed by Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion after the case starts
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in cases that end with SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and activity SW-EIC Reject for cases where activity SW-EIC Reject occurs

Name: Time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Average time for SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion compared to the duration of SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in variants involving checklist reminders
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time until SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion is performed after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation in inverted-order variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-EIC Major Revision in multi-round revision cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to transition to SW-Checklist Completion now due in delayed variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completion now due'

Name: Time of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion cycle in submissions that include Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the first occurrence of any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Total waiting time to SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in cases where Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and the end of case where activity 'Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded occurs

Name: Minimum time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to Manuscript Export Succeeded in high-performance (low total duration) variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
